{"tid":708360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"根本男人都係雞","createTime":"2018-06-19T08:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T09:10:21.000Z","uid":144546,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79f5945c1c3119a436d81845ac4c50f5ccc71685","tid":708360,"uid":144546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"罵人係雞<br />\n自己又唔試下提升自己吸引力<br />\n外型 談吐 能力 地位 <br />\n唔試下追d有錢女人？以為好易啊？<br />\n班人好似以為自己好有風骨<br />\n其實一點頭就會食到有錢女人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地咁有骨氣係因為你地連選擇嘅權利都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就退一步懶清高 話全部女人都係雞<br />\n<br />\n返工見到好多靚女<br />\n人地難得天生得靚 <br />\nkeep到自己咁fit<br />\n日日都注重自己打扮<br />\n抵人地挭到靚仔有錢仔㗎wo<br />\n班女仔自己有條件嘛<br />\n可以揾到好條件嘅男仔發展感情<br />\n唔通揾個無見識無外型無自信無錢嘅人咩<br />\n<br />\n連登仔諗埋d野同韓劇差唔多<br />\n係度ff女神會放棄一切鍾意自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6170ef67262e7a28dedec4dd527aaa742e62fa","tid":708360,"uid":144546,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"仲有唔好成日ff人地同有錢佬一齊係無感情先得㗎<br />\n大把都恩愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af49a8d260329fecff01e09517f4fa428c99ef33","tid":708360,"uid":149179,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/170519_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F170519_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bf1a975b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9e3c1cd2658f2aba90193b347359bb6e388b825","tid":708360,"uid":95478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:10:21.000Z","msg":"其實同有錢人一齊既女唔等於雞<br />\n雞係衰在無腦 同埋太勢利<br />\n狗眼看人低<br />\n只係諗住付出肉體 就得到大好前途<br />\n好有上進心同時唔想付出什麼就得到成果既就係臭雞"}]}